et due to being on bedrest because of a \nnew medical condition but was able to perform this activity prior to the current medical condition.  \n\nGG0170G Car transfer \n\nDEFINITION \n\nCAR TRANSFER \nThe ability to transfer in and out of a car or van on the passenger side.  Does not include \nthe ability to open/close door or fasten seat belt. \n\nCoding Tips", "type": "Document"}}